    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Using Rheostat as our default implementation will introduce some inconsistencies between our classnames and theirs. \nTrying not to complicate things before the first release, I propose that we do not provide a Slider but instead explain how to connect easily to an existing one. \n\nAs for the design (#1456) we can use Rheostat to have a complete example. \n",
